---

<section id="workshop" class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
      PDR 101 Workshop
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Come learn everything you need to start doing PDR at this two-day event.
    </p>
    
    <a 
      href="https://realworldpdr.com/pdr-101-workshop/"
      class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 uppercase tracking-wide"
    >
      learn more
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
